ntent>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-034 — CI/CD GitHub Actions (12 workflows)\n\n## 概述\n\n| 属性 | 值 |\n|------|-----|\n| AR | AR-034 |\n| Module | .github |\n| Language | YAML |\n| Size | L |\n\n---\n\n## 1. Purpose (目的)\n\n[TO BE FILLED: Define purpose for CI/CD GitHub Actions]\n\n---\n\n## 2. Scope (范围)","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-034/proposal.md","time":{"start":1775888940400,"end":1775888940410}}}}
